{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1057,"text":"Einstein said that"},{"time":2497,"text":"\"I never think about the future â€”\nit comes soon enough.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":5954,"text":"And he was right, of course."},{"time":7655,"text":"So today, I'm here to ask you to think of"},{"time":10199,"text":"how the future is happening now."},{"time":13059,"text":"Over the past 200 years, the world has experienced"},{"time":15822,"text":"two major waves of innovation."},{"time":17752,"text":"First, the Industrial Revolution"},{"time":19981,"text":"brought us machines and factories, railways,"},{"time":22502,"text":"electricity, air travel,"},{"time":24832,"text":"and our lives have never been the same."},{"time":27152,"text":"Then the Internet revolution"},{"time":29578,"text":"brought us computing power, data networks,"},{"time":32811,"text":"unprecedented access"},{"time":35146,"text":"to information and communication,"},{"time":37499,"text":"and our lives have never been the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40774,"text":"Now we are experiencing"},{"time":42387,"text":"another metamorphic change:"},{"time":44151,"text":"the industrial Internet."},{"time":46338,"text":"It brings together intelligent machines,"},{"time":49313,"text":"advanced analytics,"},{"time":50853,"text":"and the creativity of people at work."},{"time":53219,"text":"It's the marriage of minds and machines."},{"time":56419,"text":"And our lives will never be the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58975,"text":"In my current role, I see up close"},{"time":61968,"text":"how technology is beginning to transform"},{"time":64801,"text":"industrial sectors that play a huge role"},{"time":67332,"text":"in our economy and in our lives:"},{"time":69725,"text":"energy, aviation, transportation, health care."},{"time":74412,"text":"For an economist, this is highly unusual,"},{"time":76703,"text":"and it's extremely exciting,"},{"time":78242,"text":"because this is a transformation"},{"time":80131,"text":"as powerful as the Industrial Revolution and more,"},{"time":84153,"text":"and before the Industrial Revolution,"},{"time":85612,"text":"there was no economic growth to speak of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88562,"text":"So what is this industrial Internet?"},{"time":91917,"text":"Industrial machines are being equipped"},{"time":93780,"text":"with a growing number of electronic sensors"},{"time":96040,"text":"that allow them to see, hear, feel"},{"time":99489,"text":"a lot more than ever before,"},{"time":101195,"text":"generating prodigious amounts of data."},{"time":104266,"text":"Increasingly sophisticated analytics"},{"time":106233,"text":"then sift through the data,"},{"time":108074,"text":"providing insights that allow us"},{"time":110830,"text":"to operate the machines in entirely new ways,"},{"time":113864,"text":"a lot more efficiently."},{"time":115770,"text":"And not just individual machines,"},{"time":117759,"text":"but fleets of locomotives, airplanes,"},{"time":120544,"text":"entire systems like power grids, hospitals."},{"time":123716,"text":"It is asset optimization and system optimization."},{"time":127942,"text":"Of course, electronic sensors"},{"time":129952,"text":"have been around for some time,"},{"time":131657,"text":"but something has changed:"},{"time":133569,"text":"a sharp decline in the cost of sensors"},{"time":136420,"text":"and, thanks to advances in cloud computing,"},{"time":138897,"text":"a rapid decrease in the cost of storing"},{"time":141913,"text":"and processing data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144280,"text":"So we are moving to a world"},{"time":145990,"text":"where the machines we work with"},{"time":147783,"text":"are not just intelligent; they are brilliant."},{"time":152024,"text":"They are self-aware, they are predictive,"},{"time":154782,"text":"reactive and social."},{"time":158141,"text":"It's jet engines, locomotives, gas turbines,"},{"time":162099,"text":"medical devices, communicating seamlessly"},{"time":164880,"text":"with each other and with us."},{"time":167205,"text":"It's a world where information itself"},{"time":169209,"text":"becomes intelligent and comes to us"},{"time":171396,"text":"automatically when we need it"},{"time":173325,"text":"without having to look for it."},{"time":176523,"text":"We are beginning to deploy"},{"time":178050,"text":"throughout the industrial system"},{"time":180505,"text":"embedded virtualization,"},{"time":182550,"text":"multi-core processor technology,"},{"time":184752,"text":"advanced cloud-based communications,"},{"time":188192,"text":"a new software-defined machine infrastructure"},{"time":190934,"text":"which allows machine functionality"},{"time":193678,"text":"to become virtualized in software,"},{"time":196252,"text":"decoupling machine software from hardware,"},{"time":199414,"text":"and allowing us to remotely and automatically"},{"time":203021,"text":"monitor, manage and upgrade industrial assets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208345,"text":"Why does any of this matter at all?"},{"time":211479,"text":"Well first of all, it's already allowing us"},{"time":213950,"text":"to shift towards preventive,"},{"time":216151,"text":"condition-based maintenance,"},{"time":218029,"text":"which means fixing machines"},{"time":219991,"text":"just before they break,"},{"time":222279,"text":"without wasting time"},{"time":224295,"text":"servicing them on a fixed schedule."},{"time":226623,"text":"And this, in turn, is pushing us towards"},{"time":230260,"text":"zero unplanned downtime,"},{"time":232115,"text":"which means there will be no more power outages,"},{"time":234980,"text":"no more flight delays."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237020,"text":"So let me give you a few examples"},{"time":238664,"text":"of how these brilliant machines work,"},{"time":240543,"text":"and some of the examples may seem trivial,"},{"time":242841,"text":"some are clearly more profound,"},{"time":244837,"text":"but all of them are going to\nhave a very powerful impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248962,"text":"Let's start with aviation."},{"time":250916,"text":"Today, 10 percent of all flights"},{"time":253184,"text":"cancellations and delays"},{"time":255302,"text":"are due to unscheduled maintenance events."},{"time":258003,"text":"Something goes wrong unexpectedly."},{"time":260035,"text":"This results in eight billion dollars in costs"},{"time":263231,"text":"for the airline industry globally every year,"},{"time":265643,"text":"not to mention the impact on all of us:"},{"time":267945,"text":"stress, inconvenience,"},{"time":270030,"text":"missed meetings as we sit helplessly"},{"time":272925,"text":"in an airport terminal."},{"time":274834,"text":"So how can the industrial Internet help here?"},{"time":278252,"text":"We've developed a preventive maintenance system"},{"time":280887,"text":"which can be installed on any aircraft."},{"time":282877,"text":"It's self-learning and able to predict issues"},{"time":286128,"text":"that a human operator would miss."},{"time":289084,"text":"The aircraft, while in flight,"},{"time":291438,"text":"will communicate with technicians on the ground."},{"time":293788,"text":"By the time it lands, they will already know"},{"time":295748,"text":"if anything needs to be serviced."},{"time":298234,"text":"Just in the U.S., a system like this can prevent"},{"time":301850,"text":"over 60,000 delays and cancellations every year,"},{"time":305557,"text":"helping seven million passengers"},{"time":307519,"text":"get to their destinations on time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310055,"text":"Or take healthcare."},{"time":311708,"text":"Today, nurses spend an average"},{"time":313439,"text":"of 21 minutes per shift"},{"time":316082,"text":"looking for medical equipment."},{"time":317775,"text":"That seems trivial, but it's less time spent"},{"time":322158,"text":"caring for patients."},{"time":324867,"text":"St. Luke's Medical Center in Houston, Texas,"},{"time":327741,"text":"which has deployed industrial Internet technology"},{"time":330668,"text":"to electronically monitor and connect"},{"time":332733,"text":"patients, staff and medical equipment,"},{"time":335932,"text":"has reduced bed turnaround times"},{"time":338242,"text":"by nearly one hour."},{"time":339977,"text":"If you need surgery, one hour matters."},{"time":342787,"text":"It means more patients can be treated,"},{"time":345114,"text":"more lives can be saved."},{"time":347104,"text":"Another medical center, in Washington state,"},{"time":350068,"text":"is piloting an application that allows"},{"time":351956,"text":"medical images from city scanners and MRIs"},{"time":355049,"text":"to be analyzed in the cloud,"},{"time":357164,"text":"developing better analytics"},{"time":359801,"text":"at a lower cost."},{"time":362362,"text":"Imagine a patient"},{"time":363986,"text":"who has suffered a severe trauma,"},{"time":365420,"text":"and needs the attention of several specialists:"},{"time":368175,"text":"a neurologist, a cardiologist,"},{"time":369984,"text":"an orthopedic surgeon."},{"time":371595,"text":"If all of them can have instantaneous\nand simultaneous access"},{"time":374921,"text":"to scans and images as they are taken,"},{"time":377707,"text":"they will be able to deliver better healthcare faster."},{"time":382405,"text":"So all of this translates into better health outcomes,"},{"time":385483,"text":"but it can also deliver substantial economic benefits."},{"time":388923,"text":"Just a one-percent reduction in existing inefficiencies"},{"time":392409,"text":"could yield savings of over 60 billion dollars"},{"time":395915,"text":"to the healthcare industry worldwide,"},{"time":398712,"text":"and that is just a drop in the sea"},{"time":401071,"text":"compared to what we need to do to make healthcare"},{"time":403807,"text":"affordable on a sustainable basis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406228,"text":"Similar advances are happening in energy,"},{"time":408486,"text":"including renewable energy."},{"time":410966,"text":"Wind farms equipped with new\nremote monitorings and diagnostics"},{"time":415659,"text":"that allow wind turbines to talk to each other"},{"time":418254,"text":"and adjust the pitch of their\nblades in a coordinated way,"},{"time":422103,"text":"depending on how the wind is blowing,"},{"time":424222,"text":"can now produce electricity at a cost"},{"time":426198,"text":"of less than five cents per kilowatt/hour."},{"time":429376,"text":"Ten years ago, that cost was 30 cents,"},{"time":431393,"text":"six times as much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433345,"text":"The list goes on, and it will grow fast,"},{"time":436249,"text":"because industrial data are\nnow growing exponentially."},{"time":438950,"text":"By 2020, they will account for over 50 percent"},{"time":441802,"text":"of all digital information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444030,"text":"But this is not just about data, so let me switch gears"},{"time":447209,"text":"and tell you how this is impacting already"},{"time":450050,"text":"the jobs we do every day,"},{"time":451493,"text":"because this new wave of innovation"},{"time":453214,"text":"is bringing about new tools and applications"},{"time":456330,"text":"that will allow us to collaborate"},{"time":458846,"text":"in a smarter and faster way,"},{"time":460416,"text":"making our jobs not just more efficient"},{"time":463549,"text":"but more rewarding."},{"time":465338,"text":"Imagine a field engineer arriving at the wind farm"},{"time":468242,"text":"with a handheld device telling her"},{"time":469928,"text":"which turbines need servicing."},{"time":472226,"text":"She already has all the spare parts,"},{"time":473704,"text":"because the problems were diagnosed in advanced."},{"time":476246,"text":"And if she faces an unexpected issue,"},{"time":478720,"text":"the same handheld device will allow her to"},{"time":481323,"text":"communicate with colleagues at the service center,"},{"time":483831,"text":"let them see what she sees,"},{"time":485931,"text":"transmit data that they can run through diagnostics,"},{"time":488686,"text":"and they can stream videos that will guide her,"},{"time":490983,"text":"step by step, through whatever complex procedure"},{"time":493351,"text":"is needed to get the machines back up and running."},{"time":495813,"text":"And their interaction gets documented"},{"time":497829,"text":"and stored in a searchable database."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502246,"text":"Let's stop and think about this for a minute,"},{"time":504001,"text":"because this is a very important point."},{"time":505722,"text":"This new wave of innovation is fundamentally"},{"time":507948,"text":"changing the way we work."},{"time":510427,"text":"And I know that many of you will be concerned \nabout the impact that innovation might have on jobs."},{"time":515627,"text":"Unemployment is already high,"},{"time":517124,"text":"and there is always a fear \nthat innovation will destroy jobs."},{"time":520360,"text":"And innovation is disruptive."},{"time":522491,"text":"But let me stress two things here."},{"time":524944,"text":"First, we've already lived through"},{"time":526875,"text":"mechanization of agriculture,\nautomation of industry,"},{"time":529638,"text":"and employment has gone up,"},{"time":531663,"text":"because innovation is fundamentally about growth."},{"time":533956,"text":"It makes products more affordable."},{"time":535849,"text":"It creates new demand, new jobs."},{"time":538509,"text":"Second, there is a concern that in the future,"},{"time":541091,"text":"there will only be room for engineers,"},{"time":543247,"text":"data scientists, and other highly-specialized workers."},{"time":546267,"text":"And believe me, as an economist, I am also scared."},{"time":549836,"text":"But think about it:"},{"time":551555,"text":"Just as a child can easily figure out"},{"time":554174,"text":"how to operate an iPad,"},{"time":555930,"text":"so a new generation of mobile and intuitive"},{"time":558055,"text":"industrial applications will make life easier"},{"time":560779,"text":"for workers of all skill levels."},{"time":563198,"text":"The worker of the future will be more like Iron Man"},{"time":566400,"text":"than the Charlie Chaplin of \"Modern Times.\""},{"time":569526,"text":"And to be sure, new high-skilled jobs will be created:"},{"time":572570,"text":"mechanical digital engineers who understand"},{"time":574446,"text":"both the machines and the data;"},{"time":576578,"text":"managers who understand their industry"},{"time":578861,"text":"and the analytics and can reorganize the business"},{"time":581722,"text":"to take full advantage of the technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584844,"text":"But now let's take a step back."},{"time":587160,"text":"Let's look at the big picture."},{"time":589204,"text":"There are people who argue that today's innovation"},{"time":591627,"text":"is all about social media and silly games,"},{"time":593976,"text":"with nowhere near the transformational power"},{"time":595866,"text":"of the Industrial Revolution."},{"time":597945,"text":"They say that all the growth-enhancing innovations"},{"time":600700,"text":"are behind us."},{"time":602126,"text":"And every time I hear this, I can't help thinking that"},{"time":605440,"text":"even back in the Stone Age,"},{"time":607408,"text":"there must have been a group of cavemen"},{"time":609697,"text":"sitting around a fire one day"},{"time":611576,"text":"looking very grumpy,"},{"time":613102,"text":"and looking disapprovingly\nat another group of cavemen"},{"time":615828,"text":"rolling a stone wheel up and down a hill,"},{"time":617997,"text":"and saying to each other,"},{"time":619806,"text":"\"Yeah, this wheel thing,"},{"time":622087,"text":"cool toy, sure, but compared to fire,"},{"time":624878,"text":"it will have no impact."},{"time":626994,"text":"The big discoveries are all behind us.\""},{"time":629318,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631205,"text":"This technological revolution"},{"time":632753,"text":"is as inspiring and transformational"},{"time":635281,"text":"as anything we have ever seen."},{"time":637294,"text":"Human creativity and innovation\nhave always propelled us forward."},{"time":640684,"text":"They've created jobs."},{"time":642131,"text":"They've raised living standards."},{"time":643520,"text":"They've made our lives"},{"time":645323,"text":"healthier and more rewarding."},{"time":647383,"text":"And the new wave of innovation"},{"time":648626,"text":"which is beginning to sweep through industry"},{"time":650976,"text":"is no different."},{"time":652598,"text":"In the U.S. alone, the industrial Internet"},{"time":654614,"text":"could raise average income by 25 to 40 percent"},{"time":658554,"text":"over the next 15 years,"},{"time":660246,"text":"boosting growth to rates we\nhaven't seen in a long time,"},{"time":662915,"text":"and adding between 10 and 15\ntrillion dollars to global GDP."},{"time":666859,"text":"That is the size of the entire U.S. economy today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671112,"text":"But this is not a foregone conclusion."},{"time":673623,"text":"We are just at the beginning of this transformation,"},{"time":675618,"text":"and there will be barriers to break,"},{"time":677474,"text":"obstacles to overcome."},{"time":679160,"text":"We will need to invest in the new technologies."},{"time":681701,"text":"We will need to adapt organizations\nand managerial practices."},{"time":685410,"text":"We will need a robust cybersecurity approach"},{"time":688304,"text":"that protects sensitive information\nand intellectual property"},{"time":692047,"text":"and safeguards critical infrastructure\nfrom cyberattacks."},{"time":695287,"text":"And the education system will need to evolve"},{"time":697524,"text":"to ensure students are equipped with the right skills."},{"time":700732,"text":"It's not going to be easy,"},{"time":702467,"text":"but it is going to be worth it."},{"time":705114,"text":"The economic challenges facing us are hard,"},{"time":708662,"text":"but when I walk the factory floor,"},{"time":710758,"text":"and I see how humans and brilliant machines"},{"time":713346,"text":"are becoming interconnected,"},{"time":715064,"text":"and I see the difference this makes"},{"time":717138,"text":"in a hospital, in an airport,"},{"time":719704,"text":"in a power generation plant, I'm not just optimistic,"},{"time":722385,"text":"I'm enthusiastic."},{"time":723993,"text":"This new technological revolution is upon us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727447,"text":"So think about the future â€”\nit will be here soon enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":730641,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":733326,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}